## üì¶ Installation and Launch

To run the project on your computer:

1. **Download the RAR file:**
* download the file from the repository
   

3. **Open the project in Unity:**
* Make sure that you have the appropriate version of Unity installed (see above).
    * Open the Unity Hub, click "Add" and select the project folder.

4. **Run:**
* In the Unity editor, set up the scenes (Main Scene, Game Scene)
    * Press the "Play" button.
